    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Branch of electrical engineering that deals with practical applications of electronics, primarily with the design, manufacture, and operation of electronic devices and systems.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
